CommentBlocks.Comment:
Command queue has 32 entries
Each entry is 2 bytes:
Byte 0 : Command number (e.g. draw string)
Byte 1 : Parameter for command (e.g. string number)
The 'I' of Konami and its attribute are stored here

First half of sprite RAM
24 sprites, 2 bytes per sprite

For each sprite:
byte 0: XPos
byte 1: Sprite definition

Second half of sprite RAM
24 sprites, 2 bytes per sprite

For each sprite:
byte 0 : Attributes
   bits 0-5 : Colour Scheme
   bit 6 : Flip X
   bit 7 : Flip Y
byte 1: Y Position
